ZH: 我们要拐左边。
EN: We need to turn left.
ZH: 他在街角被人拐走了。
EN: He was kidnapped at the street corner.
ZH: 请不要拐弯马路。
EN: Please do not make a U-turn.
ZH: 小偷拐到了小巷里。
EN: The thief turned into the alley.
ZH: 他们在十字路口拐了错方向。
EN: They turned the wrong way at the intersection.
ZH: 我们要在这个标志处拐右。
EN: We need to turn right at this sign.
ZH: 驾驶员一不小心就拐错了方向。
EN: The driver accidentally turned in the wrong direction.
ZH: 她被人拐到了图书馆。
EN: She was taken to the library by someone.
ZH: 你确定我们要拐左还是要直走？
EN: Are you sure we need to turn left or keep going straight?
ZH: 这个转盘处容易拐错。
EN: It is easy to make a wrong turn at this roundabout.
ZH: 拐弯的时候要注意前方的车辆。
EN: Pay attention to the vehicles ahead when making a turn.
ZH: 小心拐角处的危险。
EN: Be careful of the danger at the corner.
ZH: 她总是喜欢拐很多弯。
EN: She always likes to take a lot of twists and turns.
ZH: 他拐弯时没有看到前面的行人。
EN: He didn't see the pedestrians ahead when making the turn.
ZH: 拐弯速度过快会产生危险。
EN: Turning too fast can be dangerous.
ZH: 拐弯时要用车灯示意。
EN: Use your turn signals when making a turn.
ZH: 拐弯要遵守交通规则。
EN: Follow the traffic rules when making a turn.
ZH: 他被拐到了陌生的城镇。
EN: He was taken to a strange town.
